<div style="color: #374151;">
  <h2 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome to SEAS, {{name}}!</h2>
  
  <p style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">
    Thank you for registering. To complete taking your application to the School of Engineering and Applied Sciences, please verify your email address.
  </p>
  
  <p style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 15px;">
    Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to activate your account:
  </p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <div style="display: inline-block; background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #111827; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 4px; border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;">
      {{otp}}
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
    This code is valid for exactly <strong>15 minutes</strong>.
  </p>
  
  <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 30px;">
    If you did not initiate this registration, please ignore this email.
  </p>
  
  <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; border-radius: 4px;">
    <p style="color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 13px; margin: 0;">
      <strong>Security Note:</strong> SEAS Staff will never ask for your verification code. Do not share it with anyone.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
